                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 882.42/7.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of Liberia</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Monrovia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-10-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 22, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Consul General Lyon authorized receive Donovan fund and release Society.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">President Barclay</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
